PewterCity_Gym_Text_BrockIntro::
# 5 "data/maps/PewterCity_Gym/scripts.pory"
	.string "So, you're here. I'm BROCK. I'm PEWTER's\n"
	.string "GYM LEADER.\p"
	.string "My rock-hard willpower is evident even\n"
	.string "in my POKéMON.\p"
	.string "My POKéMON are all rock hard, and have\n"
	.string "true-grit determination.\p"
	.string "That's right - my POKéMON are all the\n"
	.string "ROCK type!\p"
	.string "Fuhaha! You're going to challenge me\n"
	.string "knowing that you'll lose?\p"
	.string "That's the TRAINER's honor that\n"
	.string "compels you to challenge me.\p"
	.string "Fine, then! Show me your best!{PLAY_BGM}{MUS_RG_GYM}$"

PewterCity_Gym_Text_BrockDefeat::
# 9 "data/maps/PewterCity_Gym/scripts.pory"
	.string "I took you for granted, and so I lost.\p"
	.string "As proof of your victory, I confer on\n"
	.string "you this…the official POKéMON\l"
	.string "LEAGUE BOULDERBADGE.\p"
	.string "{FONT_NORMAL}{PLAYER} received the BOULDERBADGE\n"
	.string "from BROCK!{PAUSE_MUSIC}{PLAY_BGM}{MUS_OBTAIN_BADGE}{PAUSE 0xFE}{PAUSE 0x56}{RESUME_MUSIC}\p"
	.string "{FONT_MALE}Just having the BOULDERBADGE makes\n"
	.string "your POKéMON more powerful.\p"
	.string "It also enables the use of the move\n"
	.string "FLASH outside of battle.\p"
	.string "Of course, a POKéMON must know the\n"
	.string "move FLASH to use it.$"

