PewterCity_Gym_Text_ExplainTM39::
# 21 "data/maps/PewterCity_Gym/scripts.pory"
	.string "A TM, Technical Machine, contains a\n"
	.string "technique for POKéMON.\p"
	.string "Using a TM teaches the move it contains\n"
	.string "to a POKéMON.\p"
	.string "A TM is good for only one use.\p"
	.string "So, when you use one, pick the POKéMON\n"
	.string "carefully.\p"
	.string "Anyways… TM39 contains ROCK TOMB.\p"
	.string "It hurls boulders at the foe and lowers\n"
	.string "its SPEED.$"

